{"tid":1387806,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"月尾喇林鄭月娥又出糧啦，乜都唔做又四十幾萬一個月啦","createTime":"2019-07-30T15:11:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T15:27:04.000Z","uid":135867,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4cf0128b2039c68ae712120471f4993f3fb13e46","tid":1387806,"uid":135867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T15:11:37.000Z","msg":"【揚威國際】美媒比較全球領導人薪酬　林鄭高居第二位<br />\n<br />\n有美國傳媒比較全球國家和地區元首的薪酬，特首林鄭月娥以年薪 56.84萬美元（約 443 萬港元），成為全球第二高薪的領導人，但根據資料，林鄭月娥月薪其實是 41.65萬港元，年薪接近 500 萬港元，即約 64 萬美元，但並無影響她在全球領導人薪金榜的排名。<br />\n美國傳媒《USA TODAY》以 2018 年 4 月的資料，比較全球各國家和地區的領導人薪酬，打入頭十大的大部份都是歐美和大洋洲國家，但排在頭兩位都來自亞洲，其中新加坡總理李顯龍年薪高達 161 萬美元（約 1255 萬港元），年薪大約是人均 GDP 的 18 倍；<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">而香港特首林鄭月娥的年薪排全球第二，是香港人均&nbsp;GDP 約 10 倍</span></span></strong>；而美國總統特朗普就以 40 萬美元年薪排在第 4 位，但他將薪酬全部捐出，只收取 1 美元象徵薪金。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7x1uyZ7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7x1uyZ7.png&h=641e465f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9745e131cbba2b94dfdda19b6732186f909ee987","tid":1387806,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T15:12:06.000Z","msg":"對得住前線！對得住義士！<br />\n一日政府無回應 一日都要繼續抗爭！<br />\n一個都不能少！<br />\n堅持五大訴求！！！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一、徹底撤回修例<br />\n二、收回暴動定義<br />\n三、撤銷對今為所有反送中抗爭者控罪<br />\n四、徹底追究警隊濫權情況<br />\n五、以行政命令解散立法會，立即實行雙真普選<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">也試過太衝動 大件事沒計輕重<br />\n錯過悔過仍要衝 衝出困局<br />\n形象似義勇軍<span style=\"color: violet;\">(crusade)</span>般英勇<br />\n但結果有沒有停戰的溝通?<span style=\"color: violet;\">(訴求？)</span><br />\n如戴著面具<span style=\"color: violet;\">(mask)</span>去掩飾倦容<br />\n迎著炮火也依然表情輕鬆<span style=\"color: violet;\">(不屈？)</span><br />\n情緒不可激動 還若輕的舉重<br />\n來化解一切壓力似失蹤<br />\n如放下面具去也許面紅<span style=\"color: violet;\">(憤怒？)</span><br />\n乘著晚風去追尋逍遙星空<br />\n除去假的寬容 還真想不通<br />\n曾年少的青蔥 懷著理想那怕痛<span style=\"color: violet;\">(revolution)</span></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TfDAuxC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTfDAuxC.png&h=60385d7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gnOwNja.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgnOwNja.png&h=f5b7bc3c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"e43958db17cd99609caf843fc9ab58b34f214479","tid":1387806,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T15:17:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bba1b7e31c1e320a5c77de53652f6f1ee921bdf","tid":1387806,"uid":135867,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T15:21:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/B0igGzmgaVA/?igshid=1fmm1rvhzxyx3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB0igGzmgaVA%2F%3Figshid%3D1fmm1rvhzxyx3&d=RNMQoofY58y8BAaKNkwZNlyVYJ%2BaYT2AGLfERhQaW2c%3D&h=f6504f26\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB0igGzmgaVA%2F%3Figshid%3D1fmm1rvhzxyx3&h=2559bc8a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/B0igGzmgaVA/?igshid=1fmm1rvhzxyx3</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H7uoDu9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH7uoDu9.jpg&h=95764b64&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6dd0f57922cc0979f553f08aac62db744b38761e","tid":1387806,"uid":135867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T15:27:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/norm